{"tid":982134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國去年汽車銷售 20多年來首見衰退","createTime":"2019-01-15T00:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T11:41:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c12032e6f88edddb4cdcdba06df95549103bcdd","tid":982134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"中國去年汽車銷售 20多年來首見衰退<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/3592542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F3592542&d=SapV93%2BIpUVg07QGamfIC9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=698a1cfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/3592542</a><br />\n<br />\n中國汽車工業協會今天（14日）表示，中國汽車去年全年銷售下滑2.8%到2,810萬輛，這是自1990年代以來，首見的衰退。協會副秘書長師建華說，今年中國汽車業面臨的競爭更加嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n中國汽車工業協會公布的去年12月份汽車銷售統計顯示，12月單月銷售減少13%到266萬輛，其中經由經銷商銷售的乘用客車，銷量減少15.8%到223萬輛。去年全年，乘用客車銷量跌幅為4.1%，銷售量2,370萬輛。"},{"pid":"6435919a81f7a0d1c7b4b2e005ad2e2e54046344","tid":982134,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"國六車,混能,電車...<br />\n已經有報告預測 2026 左右全球90% 車行電..."},{"pid":"0d581eeb388911804542bc555db9e9971211043e","tid":982134,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6435919a81f7a0d1c7b4b2e005ad2e2e54046344","tid":982134,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"國六車,混能,電車...<br />\n已經有報告預測 2026 左右全球90% 車行電..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"電池污染問題解決左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbcc0ed2245870eab84378f71f22fc64b4ad403","tid":982134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}